 "name": "RPlog_Power_Facility_Attack",
 "title": "Power Facility Attack",
 "summary": "During elaborate New Republic fleet wargames, the Jedi Enb'Zik takes up a lookout position atop a prefab structure in an industrial mock-battlefield, straining through the Force to sense the opposing force massing nearby. The naval officer Lynae Cassius, uneasy commanding ground troops, organizes her marines into small groups and positions them per her plan, while the opfor volunteer Rivo and Captain Lofte's commando teams maneuver into concealed assault positions. The Bothan scout Tarkis ranges ahead with his spotting scope as both sides settle into the tense, jittery quiet before engagement. The log captures the careful pre-battle positioning and nerves of a simulated assault on a power facility.",
